FuncDef: This command displays service information using the range of ingress labels.

ParaDef.Info: Displays the starting ingress label value for which to display services using the label range. If only ingress-label1 is specified, services only using ingress-label1 are displayed. Values-0, 2048 to 131071.
Displays the ending ingress label value for which to display services using the label range. Values-2048 to 131071. ParamDefault: Default- The ingress-label1 value.
